msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "If you have a voice assistant in your home or on your phone, have you ever been concerned that someone from the company could listen to your voice recordings?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.8fb086c3-9256-4375-bf59-a6be385f8838"
msgid ""
"UPDATE: Apple now has an opt-in for human review with iOS 13.2. It also gives users the option to delete their Siri voice recordings. The images below have been updated accordingly.<br/><br/> In "
"September 2019, <a id=\"a1\">Google reactivated its human review program for the Google Home, now with user consent</a>.<br/><br/> Read on to find out how to change your settings."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.8fb086c3-9256-4375-bf59-a6be385f8838"
msgid "If you have a voice assistant in your home or on your phone, have you ever been concerned that someone from the company could listen to your voice recordings?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.8fb086c3-9256-4375-bf59-a6be385f8838"
msgid "Recent news coverage confirms that suspicion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.8fb086c3-9256-4375-bf59-a6be385f8838"
msgid ""
"At the end of July, <a id=\"a1\">The Guardian reported</a> that people at Apple were regularly listening to recordings of deeply personal events such as conversations with doctors, sexual "
"encounters, and other moments. While the effort was designed as a quality control measure, users likely had no idea that some of their utterances were being recorded and reviewed by humans."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.8fb086c3-9256-4375-bf59-a6be385f8838"
msgid ""
"Since then, <a id=\"a1\">Apple has temporarily suspended its human review program</a>. Google has been forced to pause its own review program in the EU and Amazon is now giving users the ability to "
"opt-out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.8fb086c3-9256-4375-bf59-a6be385f8838"
msgid "Mozilla has put together a guide for you to change your privacy settings on voice assistants."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.276796c1-5bca-4e63-bea2-fb73bff15f43.altText"
msgid "Which voice assistants use human review of recordings"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.ccbde4a2-5176-4a4a-af4c-f0cdf1fb0f66.altText"
msgid "Amazon Alexa opt out"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.c4685337-c26e-4e63-b39b-c78d141fb9bf.altText"
msgid "Google Home opt out"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.550eae5c-0080-461d-b662-25afa3dd8987.altText"
msgid "Siri opt out"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.f086d032-782f-44f8-96d4-1db12672bebf"
msgid "Even with these additional privacy controls, there are still a number of concerns raised by these programs that haven’t yet been resolved. Some of those concerns are:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.f086d032-782f-44f8-96d4-1db12672bebf"
msgid ""
"For users who don’t opt-out, workers at Amazon and Google are still listening to a small segment of recordings from people’s smart voice assistants and despite efforts to anonymize that data, <a "
"id=\"a1\">recordings can contain sensitive and personally identifiable information</a>. Apple does a good job of clearly explaining how user data is stored and analyzed if users do opt-in, but it "
"too <a id=\"a2\">has a human review program</a> that even with its strong precautions for anonymization could give workers snippets of voice recordings containing personally identifable information."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.f086d032-782f-44f8-96d4-1db12672bebf"
msgid ""
"In many cases, recordings were made even without someone saying the wake word (“<a id=\"a1\">Hey Google</a>”) or because they said something that sounded similar to the wake word (<a id=\"a2\">such "
"as “Syria” – alerting Apple’s Siri</a>). People may not have known they were being recorded once the device was triggered to listen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.f086d032-782f-44f8-96d4-1db12672bebf"
msgid ""
"Until recent reporting on this issue, <a id=\"a1\">these review programs were not clearly disclosed to users</a> and some like Amazon’s did not give users the ability to opt in/out. What’s more, "
"news continues to break that other companies like <a id=\"a2\">Facebook</a> are also employing human review of users’ voice content without previous disclosure. This raises questions about what "
"meaningful consent should look like when people’s data is used to train a model to improve the product."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.f086d032-782f-44f8-96d4-1db12672bebf"
msgid ""
"We will keep monitoring the developments on the issue, and of course advocate for disclosure and stronger privacy protections in publications like our <a id=\"a1\"><i>Privacy Not Included</i></a> "
"guide and more. But in the meantime,<b> it is important that consumers like you know how to set the privacy settings for your own voice assistant.<br/></b><br/> <b>After you change your own "
"settings, will you use the share buttons below to share the graphics with your friends and family?</b>"
msgstr ""

